subject: Re: "Quikscript Outpost" at new location, https://quikscript.neocities.org/quik.htm
msgSnippet: Yes, unfortunately, the free version of neocities is very strict on what file types are to be permitted. I thought that .TTF files were allowed but,
messageBody: Yes, unfortunately, the free version of neocities is very strict on what file types are to be permitted. I thought that .TTF files were allowed but, apparently, they aren't. I am working on a better solution and I will post on here when I have found one. Thank you for viewing my website and if you have any more comments or concerns about the website, please let me know. Thank you.
